description:
Add the excellent style of Nijijourney Default mode to your model!

Bright, vivid, elegant, good generalization,

The Default style is softer than the expressive style

This model is trained using 140+ niji Default mode images

Negative embedding such as aid291 or badhandv4 is recommended
